This is a port of the mic module for the Intel Xeon Phi Coprocessor for linux-3.12

mpss-modules-3.1.2 compiles fine on linux-3.12.3, untested.

to install, edit (if needed) and execute "install.sh"

if you want to help test different kernel versions, read on:

assuming that mps-modules is in your home directory, simply execute the
build.sh script from the linux directory from which you configured and
module_install'ed the version you like to compile the module for:

for example version 3.10.0:

# cd linux-3.10.0
# ~/mpss-modules/build.sh

not all tested but compiles fine with following vanilla kernels:

linux-2.6.32.60
